msgctxt "4533"
msgid "ああ。俺はいつでもいい。"
msgstr "Oh. I'm always fine."

msgctxt "4558"
msgid ""
"もともとこの街で生きていた\n"
"「斎藤一」としての生活は偽りのものだ……"
msgstr "Life as \"Saito Hajime\" who originally lived in this city is false ..."

msgctxt "4627"
msgid "別れを惜しむほどのものでもない。"
msgstr "It's not something to spare."

msgctxt "4660"
msgid "おりょうちゃんは？　あの子はどないするんや。"
msgstr "What about Oryo-chan? That child isn't going."

msgctxt "4705"
msgid ""
"どうもこうもない。\n"
"……あいつだってこれ以上、京の街に\n"
"束縛される必要はないんだ。"
msgstr ""
"There is no such thing. ... he doesn't have to be tied up in the city of "
"Kyoto anymore."

msgctxt "4788"
msgid ""
"これからは好きな場所に行き、\n"
"好きなように生きる権利がある。"
msgstr ""
"From now on, you have the right to go wherever you like and live as you "
"like."

msgctxt "4849"
msgid ""
"まあな。\n"
"……せやけどあの子にとってはそれが、\n"
"あの寺田屋なんとちゃうか？"
msgstr "Well. ...... But for that child, what is that Teradaya?"

msgctxt "4924"
msgid ""
"せやからお前を探っていたことがバレたあとも、\n"
"逃げ出さんとあの場所でお前のことを待ち続けた。\n"
"そうやろ？"
msgstr ""
"Even after I found out that I was searching for you from Saya, I kept "
"waiting for you at that place with Mr. Escape. Yeah?"

msgctxt "5029"
msgid "さあな……"
msgstr "I do not know……"

msgctxt "5040"
msgid "おりょうちゃんはなぁ、ワシらと同じや……"
msgstr "Oryo-chan is the same as me ..."

msgctxt "5081"
msgid ""
"本当の自分とはちゃう、もう１人の自分を演じて\n"
"生きていかなアカン立場やった。"
msgstr ""
"I played the other self, who is different from my true self, and took the "
"position of Akan to live."

msgctxt "5158"
msgid ""
"ワシ思うんや……　本当の姿と仮の姿。\n"
"そのどっちもが、ホンマの自分自身なんやと。"
msgstr ""
"I don't think ... Real and temporary. Both of them are Honma's own self."

msgctxt "5239"
msgid ""
"せやからあの子にとっちゃ、斎藤一に惚れ、\n"
"斎藤一の背中を追った日々は、偽りない日々\n"
"やったんや……"
msgstr ""
"The days when I fell in love with Saito Hajime and chased Saito Hajime's "
"back were true days ..."

msgctxt "5343"
msgid ""
"一（はじめ）ちゃん。\n"
"「斎藤一」としてのお前は、決して\n"
"偽りなんかやなかった。"
msgstr "Ichi (beginning) -chan. You as \"Saito Hajime\" never lied."

msgctxt "5422"
msgid ""
"斎藤一はこの時代、この瞬間、\n"
"確かに新選組三番隊隊長として生きてたんや。\n"
"この京で。"
msgstr ""
"Hajime Saito certainly lived as the captain of the Shinsengumi 3rd division "
"at this moment. In this Kyo."

msgctxt "5507"
msgid "それを偽りの一言で捨ててまってはアカン。"
msgstr "It's Akan to throw it away in a false word."

msgctxt "5553"
msgid ""
"ちゃんとおりょうちゃんと最後のお別れくらい\n"
"してきいや。\n"
"……出立は明日の朝や。まだ間に合う。"
msgstr ""
"I don't want to say goodbye to Ryo-chan. ...... I'm leaving tomorrow "
"morning. It's not too late yet."

msgctxt "5650"
msgid "ああ……　分かった。有難うな、沖田の兄さん。"
msgstr "Oh ... I see. Thank you, Okita's older brother."

msgctxt "5695"
msgid "なんやそれ。兄さんって。"
msgstr "Somehow that. What is your brother?"

msgctxt "5720"
msgid ""
"あんたにはずっと救われてきた……\n"
"俺にとってあんたは兄弟みたいなもんだってことだ。"
msgstr "You've been saved for a long time ... You're like a brother to me."

msgctxt "5803"
msgid ""
"なんや少し恥ずかしいのぅ。\n"
"ま、ええ。とにかくちゃんと最後のケジメくらい、\n"
"つけてこいや。"
msgstr ""
"It's kind of embarrassing. Well, yeah. Anyway, just put it on for the last "
"time."

msgctxt "6819"
msgid "龍馬"
msgstr "Ryoma"

msgctxt "6886"
msgid "沖田"
msgstr "Okita"
